	<!-- message -->
	<p><b>Disclaimer</b><br />
The following is my personal analysis of the current state of the high end shaman. It does not necessarily represent the views of other shaman who post here or of the Crucible as a whole.<br />
<br />
It is written from the point of view of a post-time shaman. As such it deals mainly with high end issues. Please do not attempt to apply my conclusions to such places as BoT, Cazic Thule etc.<br />
<br />
It is applicable for parts of PoP, hard LDoN adventures, LDoN raids and GoD, especially the single groups trials.<br />
<br />
<br />
<b>Thanks to</b> Ceno, Flabbo, Gardeltron, Gloriana, Jaffo, Litgruv, Sithrax and whoever I may have forgotten.<br />
<i>I have stolen a lot of ideas from a lot of different people for my proposals. If you think I forgot to credit you please PM me and I will add your name.</i></p>
	
	
	
	
