	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p><b>What to do in the future ?</b><br />
- Do not try to fix a class that is or seems to be overpowered by nerfing it in small steps in half a dozen different areas over six expansions.<br />
<br />
- Do not change the basic way the game is played (i.e. Luclin -> PoP) without readjusting the classes that get hurt and those who profit from the changes.<br />
<br />
- Do not create horribly one-sided content such as the whole one group content of GoD (so far). Even fundamentally balanced classes have issues when they have been balanced around content that no longer exists (i.e. Knight classes not being able to tank nameds in GoD).</p>
	
	
	
