	<p>yes this is a great post and does comment on most the problems faced.<br />
alot really only need minor changes to spells we already have, for instance if malos had half the cast time and slow didnt have the 6 second recast time, this would mean we could have more time to heal/dps.  As for our cold nuke, although i would wish for higher amount, if they again halved the cast time then our dps would double for short fights, making it decent if not great.<br />
Dots just go out the window, there useless in less than 1 minute fights. necro must have the same problem (but least thier other dd spells are much more effective and pets) we need dots that work like bane (30 sec high damage per tick), though often even this will not do full damage. but if you speed up our debuff so that we can debuff a mob in 5 sec instead of 15, then it might.<br />
The only thing that wont be helped but just decreaseing cast time is our heal. We should have go an u/g to this for our quick heal to about 1.7k .<br />
<br />
but as said great post, i think we should direct benlo here. to get some ideas. also should be said that up to 60 (non lodn or pop) we are ok, however past 50 some changes for some spell would still help for pop and lodn. most problem i see though are post 60. (but dots are wrong from about 50 onwards)</p>
	
	
	
	
