SV is 225hp's and 40 atk<br />
Infusion + single buffs+tureptant spirit will max out stats to be sure<br />
Ferocity = +65 to all saves, 150 atk and 40 sta.<br />
Nice 9mana/9hp regen from SD<br />
<br />
Lets see here, that is:<br />
620hps<br />
Probably capped stats<br />
190 atk (more if melee)<br />
65 to all saves<br />
9mana/9hp regen<br />
40% haste<br />
<br />
We can do:<br />
544hps<br />
Capped stats<br />
140 atk (more if melee)<br />
disease+poison +65, others +40<br />
60% haste<br />
<br />
As the *super buffers* we are getting outbuffed by our damn bastard child hybrid class?  Does anyone see anything wrong with this?<br />
<br />
