<br />
We are no longer the buff kings.<br />
<br />
Today, mana cap increase/mana regen, HP cap increase and ATK+ are the king and we are near last in two of those.  Yeah, I can buff my SK to 400 str/sta...but it is capped at 270 now for him, what good is that?<br />
<br />
If they want to see the REAL power of FA and our buffs, up the stat cap to 600 or so and see people running around with 500+ STR/DEX with FA and THEN you will have something to be in awe about.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
