	<p>Hmmm...with replen I'm regenning 46hp/tick, or 460hp/min, 1380hp/3minute, in other words it takes care of ~70% of each AA canni. With regen focus effects it would be more. That isnt insignificant, particularly if you are in combat and want to conserve mana or cant spare the time to Q. I'm seldom at full health if my mana bar isnt full, so it works in down time as well.</p>
	
	
	
